ec2-consistent-snapshot (0.1-9) karmic; urgency=low

  * Replace "/etc/init.d/mysql stop" with "mysqladmin shutdown".
    (closes: bug#497557)
  * Document --description option which was added earlier.
    (closes: bug#487692)
  * Read MySQL "host" parameter from .my.cnf if provided.
    (closes: bug#485978)
  * Support quoted values in .my.cnf
    (closes: bug#454184)
  * Require Net::Amazon::EC2 version 0.11 or higher.
    (closes: bug#490686)
  * Require xfsprogs package.
    (closes: bug#493420)

